Package com.epam.facultative.controller.actions.impl.general

package com.epam.facultative.controller.actions.impl.general
Containing all general actions implementations. AddAvatarAction - to add avatar to user to database AuthAction - to authorization ChangePasswordAction - to change user password in database CoursesAction - get courses list from database DownloadCoursesAction - get pdf file with courses LogOutAction - to log out MyCabinetAction - to show user`s cabinet RecoveryPasswordAction - to recovery password RegisterAction - to add student to database TeachersAction - get teachers list from database
Version:
1.0
Author:
Oleksandr Panchenko
